sequenceDiagram

participant U as User
participant F as Frontend
participant D as Django Backend
participant DB as Database
participant S as Storage

U->>F: Login Request
F->>D: Send Credentials
D->>DB: Verify User
DB-->>D: Authentication Success
D-->>F: Login Success

U->>F: Upload Image
F->>D: Send Image File
D->>D: Validate File

alt Valid Image
    D->>S: Store Image
    D->>DB: Save Metadata
    D-->>F: Upload Successful
else Invalid Image
    D-->>F: Error Response
end
